00:00:29.770 --> 00:00:31.240
especially for kids.

00:00:31.240 --> 00:00:31.930
However,

00:00:31.930 --> 00:00:34.200
as adults it doesn't have to be that way.

00:00:34.200 --> 00:00:38.150
