00:00:38.150 --> 00:00:39.060
By the way,

00:00:39.060 --> 00:00:43.510
rote memorization in cases and clear it means that you memorize something and you just

00:00:43.510 --> 00:00:44.710
memorize whether it be vocab,

00:00:44.710 --> 00:00:47.620
where there be a grammatical rule or anything along those lines,

00:00:47.620 --> 00:00:51.170
and you memorize it over time because it's something that needs to be remembered.

