00:01:04.550 --> 00:01:07.580
then vocab is memorized.

00:01:07.580 --> 00:01:09.400
But through rote memorization,

00:01:09.400 --> 00:01:10.730
it's a great way to memorize it.

00:01:10.730 --> 00:01:11.120
Of course,

00:01:11.120 --> 00:01:12.710
you can learn it in conversation.

00:01:12.710 --> 00:01:13.550
