and,

00:01:24.370 --> 00:01:24.940
ah,

00:01:24.940 --> 00:01:27.050
chances are hardly any of it will stick with you.

00:01:27.050 --> 00:01:33.590
And so rote memorization is actually a great way to learn vocab and grammar and to get the

00:01:33.590 --> 00:01:34.270
rules set.

00:01:34.270 --> 00:01:34.900
Obviously,

00:01:34.900 --> 00:01:38.990
