00:01:39.420 --> 00:01:42.270
it's quite a big challenge for many adults because we learned in the classroom.

00:01:42.270 --> 00:01:45.220
And then we have to converse with speakers as I mentioned before,

00:01:45.220 --> 00:01:45.900
because then we have.

00:01:45.900 --> 00:01:46.910
