00:01:46.910 --> 00:01:47.920
and it could be very difficult,

00:01:47.920 --> 00:01:48.250
etcetera,

00:01:48.250 --> 00:01:48.650
etcetera.

00:01:48.650 --> 00:01:50.970
But rote memorization is very important,

00:01:50.970 --> 00:01:57.460
